Overview

This dashboard shows System and Configuration overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested System and Configuration logs from Prisma Access.

It highlights the top users performing configurations, configuration events categorized by their action results, and identifies the top hostnames associated with system events. Additionally, it provides insights into the top actions linked to system events, categorizes system events by subtype, and offers essential details on configuration and system events.
